CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Megan Holdings is a company principally engaged in the development, construction and maintenance of aquaculture farms and related works. Since our inception in 2020, we have strived to establish ourselves as a trusted and experienced provider of shrimp farm related maintenance services in Malaysia. As of the date of this prospectus, we have been carrying out a series of upgrading and maintenance works for aquaculture farms, all of which are located in Tawau, Sabah, Malaysia. Complementary to our upgrading and maintenance services, we also assist customers with the design and development of new farms.
